## 5) Revision prompts that outperform full rewrites

Use targeted prompts rather than "rewrite everything":

### Diagnostic pass
```text
Line-edit this scene.
Return:
- 3 strongest lines (why they work)
- 5 weakest lines (exact replacements)
- Any cliché, vagueness, tonal drift, or POV breaks
- Where tension plateaus and how to raise it
```

### Surgical rewrite pass
```text
Rewrite only paragraphs [2,4,7].
Goals: increase subtext, cut exposition by 30%, sharpen verbs, preserve plot facts.
```

### Compression pass
```text
Reduce total word count by 12%.
Do not remove plot events. Cut redundancy, throat-clearing, and repeated emotional beats.
```

